        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Cells contain different polymerases for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"D N A\"><math alttext=\"D N A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>DNA</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> replication and transcription.</p>",
